abstract: Itsaknockout wins Fountain Youth Stakes after Upstart is disqualified for interference.
lead_paragraph: Itsaknockout was awarded a victory in the Fountain of Youth Stakes after Upstart, who had finished first, was disqualified for impeding Itsaknockout during the race.

headline.main: In Derby Warm-Up Race, a Favorite Is Disqualified
headline.print_headline: Favorite Disqualified in Warm-Up for Derby
headline.seo: Itsaknockout Wins Fountain of Youth Stakes Over Upstart
